name: EURC
public_notice: Euro Coin (EUROC) has rebranded to EURC (EURC). For more information, please refer to this announcement from the Circle Blog.

description.en: Euro Coin is a stablecoin issued by Circle under the same reserve model as USD Coin (USDC). It is designed to be stable and 100% backed by euros held in euro denominated banking accounts. An Euro Coin (EUROC) will be redeemable 1:1 for the euro currency.
